About
=====

RevRaiser is a bare-boned straight-forward on-line fund raising application. It
was written to raise funding for a laser-cutter for hackerspace [Revelation
Space][1] in The Hague, NL.

Consult subdirectory ./doc for details on installation and setup.

More information can be found on [the project wiki page][2].

